==English==
===Etymology===
Named for the great speed of the retreat;  ''[[handicap]]'' is in the horse-racing sense.
===Noun===
'''[[Benghazi]] [[Handicap]]'''
# {{slang}} The [[retreat]] of allied forces from [[Benghazi]] in North Africa in March 1941 during [[World War II]] ahead of German forces commanded by [[w:Erwin Rommel|Erwin Rommel]]. [http://www.australiansatwarfilmarchive.gov.au/aawfa/campaigns/Tobruk.html]